---
title: Carb Smart Garden Vegetable and Chicken Breast Soup with Cannellini Beans and Parmesan
description: This wholesome soup is packed with veggies that offer a natural sweetness when cooked, while hearty chicken and the herbs from the sun-dried tomato pesto and torn basil heighten the flavour impact even more.

